dc_description_s: This data represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Eau Claire County, Wisconsin in 2019. [PLSS corners within Eau Claire County, WI. The geodatabase featureclass contains point features representing original government survey section corners, quarter corners, and meander corners as well as some center of section and corners of repute.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
